        "ggM5PyQMWIe_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4509bc60-7755-4bb1-bf01-ade8debf7b92.png",
        "ggLDYJogvxV_text": "<p>90-DAY MONEY BACK GUARANTEE</p>",
        "ggnoiLlCDO__text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">If you’re not absolutely thrilled with the results, we will refund every single penny of your investment. No hassle. </span></p>",
        "ggS7aImJyob_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-57c29034-4d6a-46b9-8286-ab77c5f0b8cb.png",
        "gggjLf4dDUF_text": "<p>FREE SHIPPING</p>",
        "gg8yY22gLoi_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">We provide fast free shipping and handling for all orders.</span></p>",
        "ggYRGn3_-rs_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-00428b28-be38-4a92-add3-22f1e8e1171f.png",
        "ggtkmBCG_Es_text": "<p>GUARANTEED HIGH QUALITY</p>",
        "ggnO_gdadKG_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">Engineered for real results, built to last. Every brace is made with durable, medical-grade materials and precision stitching to deliver serious support - day after day.</span></p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_565050739282805555": {
      "type": "gp-section-565050739282805555",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "cabe26921e2b62bcc1c5aedf84e76aedbfcc8a9a6927f92bdb12860e7e56ce29_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>You’re one wear away from standing tall, walking free, and finally shutting down that relentless pain.</strong></span>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "Your Pain Isn’t Random - It’s a Warning Sign ",
        "ggvRuJ9v83P_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-48f244fe-1ee7-47b9-95ae-ede9ed840e1d.png",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "Your Pain Isn’t Random - It’s a Warning Sign ",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>That stabbing pain in your hip or lower back didn’t come from one wrong move. It built up over time - from sitting too long, poor posture, weak support muscles, and years of strain your body’s been silently absorbing.</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>Eventually, your spine shifts. Your hips misalign. And the pressure lands right on your sciatic nerve - turning every step, bend, or twist into agony.</p>",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>Pills won’t fix it. Stretching helps, but it’s not enough. Until you stop the nerve compression at its source, the pain will keep coming back.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_565050739283329843": {
      "type": "gp-section-565050739283329843",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "cd963d58033a4964303f89ab5021176aa5ab9105384d24573e0686be589551d8_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "Here’s How You Finally Fix the Problem - Not Just Numb It",
        "gg1XAFZKoNB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-d2484f7a-f767-44ae-b698-f7576d04de1b.png",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "Here’s How You Finally Fix the Problem - Not Just Numb It",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ Align Hip &amp; Back Stabilizer was built to do what painkillers and stretches can’t - stop the pressure at its source.</p>",
        "gg-RifOCijk_text": "<p>With just one wear, its advanced compression targets your lower back, hips, and sacroiliac joint - locking everything into proper alignment and taking direct pressure off the sciatic nerve.</p>",
        "gg6VOc0b2kk_text": "<p>No pills. No therapy visits. No guesswork.</p>",
        "ggFSvu4q1Qg_text": "<p>By stabilizing the muscles and ligaments around your spine and hips, it:</p>",
        "ggsFX5L6qta_text": "<p><strong>Reduces inflammation</strong></p>",
        "ggplgIk_kcW_text": "<p><strong>Improves circulation</strong></p>",
        "ggJzClcBPhP_text": "<p><strong>Prevents further nerve compression</strong></p>",
        "ggjZnI4Pmdn_text": "<p>And the best part? You don’t have to move a muscle. Just strap it on, sit back, and let your body finally recover - the way it was meant to.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_565050739282412339": {
      "type": "gp-section-565050739282412339",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "9d6c42ca52db9f493ad72c0e2d039ac03e88d978ea0a8e1a5542143b6a91740e_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Professionally Designed. Backed by Real Science.",
        "gg9y5JdW85Y_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f44680e2-de43-42ec-8625-476091f28124.png",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Professionally Designed. Backed by Real Science.",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ Align Hip &amp; Back Stabilizer is built on proven physical therapy principles.</p>",
        "ggAVlXtnnao_text": "<p><strong>Engineered by</strong> pain specialists to stabilize the hips and spine</p>",
        "ggN9leWSo1V_text": "<p><strong>Targets</strong> the root cause of sciatica and lower back pain: nerve compression</p>",
        "ggR6PQbclBZ_text": "<p><strong>Based on</strong> clinically supported compression technology</p>",
        "ggYDgNhO7t0_text": "<p><strong>Inspired by</strong> the same methods used in physical therapy clinics - now wearable at home</p>",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p>Hip braces are an effective, drug-free way to reduce pain and improve mobility in people dealing with sciatica.</p>",
        "ggmC_ttV0mJ_text": "<p>(<a href=\"https://nih.gov/\"><span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong><u>Zhang et al., Journal of Orthopaedic Surgery &amp; Research, 2018</u></strong></span></a>)</p>",
        "ggcllM8jPEK_text": "<p>Now, that same relief is as easy as strapping it on - no appointments needed.</p>",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "Real Support That Works with Your Body - Not Against It",
        "ggCRWiTBGEh_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b7cea502-5666-4b45-b79c-443cc40ad2d7.png",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "Real Support That Works with Your Body - Not Against It",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p>Pain happens when your hips and spine fall out of alignment and start compressing the sciatic nerve. That pressure builds over time - turning into burning, stabbing, or radiating pain that doesn’t go away on its own.</p>",
        "gg5A_s7vPft_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ Align Hip &amp; Back Stabilizer uses targeted compression to support your hips, spine, and surrounding muscles - helping reduce nerve pressure, increase circulation, and ease inflammation at the root.</p>",
        "ggaFHF5sugD_text": "<p>It’s lightweight, discreet, and easy to wear under clothes - no complex setup, no learning curve. Just wrap it on and let it do the work while you move, rest, or recover. The more consistently you wear it, the better you feel - and the longer relief lasts.</p>"
      }
    },
