        "checksum": "5bc05cd872450cbd4ee22437060196ab3b8c7ec716dbc9d0287985157ff38806_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggrydDXALPH_text": "What Our Customers Are Saying",
        "gg_nv0E1WSj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-7367ddd9-7e46-46e2-b6d9-c82753fe4be8.png",
        "gg029TQ7PQT_text": "<p>“I couldn’t stand or sit without pain - now I barely think about it.”</p>",
        "ggnkoHZd9S5_text": "<p>I’ve had sciatica for years and nothing ever helped long term. This brace made a difference immediately. I wear it around the house and feel so much more mobile.</p>",
        "ggmciU_MO8m_text": "<p>— Karen D., 58</p>",
        "ggx_FgcD6ei_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b420fdda-8fe1-4506-8a99-8e3ddcea98b2.png",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>“I was skeptical. But the relief was instant.”</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>I’ve tried pills, stretches, therapy - nothing lasted. I felt stupid for trying another thing , but this one actually took the edge off the pain in minutes.</p>",
        "ggReBUA1njy_text": "<p>— Jason T., 47</p>",
        "ggcIBXq5yW6_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-181172db-ea96-42e4-bc11-035d816f21e5.png",
        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>“I sleep better, walk better, and I’m not scared of the pain anymore.”</p>",
        "ggZSVoxxXVa_text": "<p>Every step used to send a shock down my leg. Now I wear this daily and I’m moving with way more confidence - even sleeping through the night again.</p>",
        "ggQgcHb_VvV_text": "<p>— Elena M., 63</p>"
      }
    },
