        "checksum": "487521c248a0a7aa0f163c9ba6d7c1af0d8fdf38b8ef5e92f57fd5b159a67418_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>Will it actually relieve my sciatica or hip pain?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>How long should I wear it each day?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>Can I wear it under my clothes?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Is it uncomfortable or restrictive?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>Do I need to be active while wearing it for it to work?</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>Yes - the SmoothSpine™ Align Hip &amp; Back Stabilizer is designed to support your lower back and hips, taking pressure off the sciatic nerve, which is a major cause of pain. Many users report noticeable relief within the first few wears.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>We recommend wearing it for 15–60 minutes a day to start, gradually increasing as your body adjusts. Many users wear it while walking, working, or relaxing at home.</p>",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>Absolutely. The SmoothSpine™ Align Hip &amp; Back Stabilizeris low-profile and designed to be worn discreetly under clothing without bulk - perfect for daily use without anyone noticing.</p>",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>Not at all. It’s made with breathable, flexible materials and adjustable straps for a snug but comfortable fit. Most users forget they’re even wearing it.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>Nope! SmoothSpine™ Align Hip &amp; Back Stabilizer works whether you're moving around or just sitting. It’s designed to support your body in any position - including while you rest or sleep.</p>"
      }
    },
